 TEIform=\"biblScope\">1271b30</biblScope> </bibl> ; at Argos, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1303a:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1303a8</biblScope> </bibl> : hence generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dependent, subject</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">περιοίκους τε καὶ οἰκέτας ἔχοντες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:547c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">547c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐξὸν . . ἅπαντας τοὺς βαρβάρους περιοίκους τῆς Ἑλλάδος καταστῆσαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg011.perseus-grc1:131\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.131</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n81790.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> geographically, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">περίοικοι, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">οἱ</gen></foreign>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">those who live on the same parallel of latitude as ourselves but</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">180</biblScope> </bibl>&lt;*&gt; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">East or West of us</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄντοικοι</foreign> (v. Addenda), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντίποδες</foreign> (qq. v.). <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1383.tlg001:16:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Gem.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.1</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1272.tlg001:1:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <